commentary: Shaheen Shah Afridi to de Kock, OUT close shout for leg before, given. De Kock reviews. commentary: Usman Shinwari to Rabada, OUT another one goes down! Boy, SA are crumbling pretty spectacularly here. Three in an over for Shinwari. commentary: Imran Tahir to Fakhar Zaman, OUT Tahir is up and running! Fakhar set himself for a slog sweep, but the shot can only get as far as van der Dussen at deep midwicket. And this is a wonderful celebration of the wicket, Tahir removing his shoe and dialling his fellow wristspinner Shamsi, who takes his own shoe off in the dug out and answers the call. The wristspinners' union!

commentary: Phehlukwayo to Imam-ul-Haq, OUT edged and gone. You could see this coming. There were a few dots, the field was up and the gaps were proving hard to find. Imam dances down, swings for the fences, and nicks through to the keeper.. And the Jo'burg crowd roars in delight. Some late cheer on a forgettable day for their team
